ons include QS experiments reaching\nmore than $2^{100}$ Feynman paths, quantum neuron implementations and solutions\nof nonlinear Schr\\\"odinger equation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Aug 2019 17:51:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Nov 2019 05:02:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 10 Jul 2020 13:42:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-13"}
