d SSG and the classifier. Extensive experiments on two public\nbenchmarks THUMOS'14 and ActivityNet1.3 demonstrate the impressive performance\nof our proposed method compared with the state-of-the-arts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Aug 2019 02:33:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-08"}
