 directly against measuring the eigenvalues. For the purposes of\ncosmological parameter estimation we advocate the use of the matrix elements,\nto avoid spurious anisotropic signals that can be generated by the eigenvalue\ndecomposition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Aug 2019 05:05:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
