 demonstrates that it incurs low overhead,\naffordable even for lowest-end embedded devices, e.g., those based on MSP430 or\nARV ATMega processors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Aug 2019 05:16:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Jan 2020 19:06:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-14"}
